---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About AiLex Consulting - AI Governance & Regulatory Affairs Authority" description="Meet Matthew Grant, Principal Consultant at AiLex Consulting. Expert guidance for EU AI Act compliance and strategic AI governance implementation. 20+ years regulatory expertise.">
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-parchment to-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
            About AiLex Consulting
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-advisory-grey">
            Expert guidance for organisations navigating AI governance requirements 
            combined with regulatory affairs mastery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Principal Profile Section -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-12 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-8">
            
            <!-- Professional Photo -->
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-4 border-european-blue shadow-lg">
                <img 
                  src="/images/matthew-grant-professional.png" 
                  alt="Matthew Grant, Principal Consultant and Founder of AiLex Consulting"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  width="192"
                  height="192"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Matthew Grant</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-european-blue font-semibold">Principal Consultant & Founder</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey italic mt-2">Scientia et Lex</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Professional Summary -->
            <div class="flex-grow">
              <div class="mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Professional Background</h3>
                <p class="text-advisory-grey mb-4">
                  Matthew Grant brings over 20 years of regulatory expertise to AI governance, 
                  having worked extensively with Grant Thornton, BDO, RSM, and Mazars on complex 
                  compliance implementations across the European financial services sector.
                </p>
                <p class="text-advisory-grey">
                  His expertise spans EU AI Act compliance, GDPR implementation, and strategic 
                  regulatory affairs, with particular strength in translating complex regulatory 
                  requirements into practical business solutions.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Key Credentials -->
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-european-blue/5 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Education</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">Advanced regulatory qualifications with specialisation in AI governance frameworks</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-innovation-indigo/5 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Experience</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">20+ years Big Four and boutique consultancy experience across Europe</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Company Overview -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-12 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-innovation-indigo to-european-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="ailex-logo text-2xl text-white font-bold">
                <span class="ai-element">AI</span><span class="lex-element">LEX</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-advisory-grey italic">Scientia et Lex - Knowledge and Law</p>
          </div>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-advisory-grey">
            <p class="mb-6">
              AiLex Consulting embodies the convergence of artificial intelligence capabilities 
              with regulatory expertise, specifically tailored for the sophisticated European 
              professional services market. Our approach bridges technological innovation with 
              legal requirements, ensuring organisations achieve compliance whilst maximising 
              strategic advantage.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6">
              The firm's positioning as the definitive European authority on AI governance 
              reflects extensive experience across diverse industry sectors combined with 
              deep understanding of regulatory frameworks. This cross-pollination of insights 
              enables systematic best practice sharing without the constraints of internal politics.
            </p>

            <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-european-blue pl-6 italic text-lg mb-6">
              "Regulatory compliance represents opportunity rather than obstacle. 
              Through systematic preparation combined with strategic thinking, organisations achieve both regulatory certainty 
              and competitive advantage."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-blue-100">
              Our approach emphasises preparation over reaction, enabling organisations to view 
              regulatory requirements as strategic opportunities rather than operational burdens.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Expertise Areas -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          
          <!-- Expertise Areas -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Core Expertise</h2>
