                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-european-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-european-blue" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">EU AI Act Mastery</h3>
                  <p class="text-advisory-grey">
                    Comprehensive understanding of Articles 6-29, risk classification methodologies, 
                    and conformity assessment procedures. Practical implementation across high-risk systems.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-innovation-indigo/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-innovation-indigo" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Financial Services Specialisation</h3>
                  <p class="text-advisory-grey">
                    Deep expertise in Consumer Duty, SM&CR, model risk management, and algorithmic 
                    decision-making within regulated financial institutions.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-compliance-green/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-compliance-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Cross-Industry Implementation</h3>
                  <p class="text-advisory-grey">
                    Proven methodology deployment across insurance, asset management, fintech, 
                    and corporate finance sectors with sector-specific adaptations.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Market Position -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Market Position</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-4 border-european-blue pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Premium Specialist</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                  Serving C-suite executives requiring sophisticated regulatory guidance 
                  with institutional-quality standards at boutique responsiveness.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-4 border-innovation-indigo pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Pan-European Authority</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                  Particular strength in EU regulatory frameworks and institutional requirements 
                  with proven track record across multiple jurisdictions.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-4 border-compliance-green pl-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Strategic Partnership Approach</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                  Long-term relationships focusing on sustainable competitive advantage 
                  through proactive compliance and strategic positioning.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Choose AiLex -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-slate-200 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">Why Choose AiLex</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
