                His experience spans Big Four consultancies (Grant Thornton, BDO, RSM, Mazars) and includes direct 
                implementation of EU AI Act compliance across multiple regulated sectors.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">How does AiLex differ from Big Four consultancies?</h3>
              <p class="text-advisory-grey">
