                Comprehensive EU AI Act mastery combined with practical implementation experience 
                across diverse regulatory frameworks and institutional requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-innovation-indigo/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-innovation-indigo" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zM3 10a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM14 9a1 1 0 00-1 1v6a1 1 0 001 1h2a1 1 0 001-1v-6a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
