              <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">
                Advanced understanding of AI system architecture, model risk management, 
                and technical documentation requirements for regulatory compliance.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-compliance-green/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
